### Get all movies
GET http://localhost:3004/movies

### Get movie by ID
GET http://localhost:3004/movies/5f63bb9f9c4e6f001f7e9a7c

### Add a new movie
POST http://localhost:3004/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "The Dark Knight",
    "director": "Christopher Nolan",
    "year": 2008
}

### Update movie by ID
PUT http://localhost:3004/movies/5f63bb9f9c4e6f001f7e9a7c
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "The Dark Knight Rises",
    "director": "Christopher Nolan",
    "year": 2012
}

### Delete movie by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3004/movies/5f63bb9f9c4e6f001f7e9a7c
